Locked Up feature activates when 3 or more Locked Up symbols appear on the same row in the main game.
During the Locked Up feature, only Locked Up symbols and Golden Locked Up symbols will appear on the reels.
The Locked Up symbols on the row are moved together and assigned a random coin win value of 1-10 x bet value.
All Locked Up symbols from the main game stay on the game area and move towards the center forming a cluster.
The Locked Up and Golden Locked Up symbols spin independently but simultaneously on the reels.
During every spin if new Locked Up or Golden Locked Up symbols appear, creating a new winning cluster or adding to an existing cluster, the number of remaining spins resets to 3.
When a Locked Up symbol lands adjacent to a winning cluster, a random coin win value of 1-10 x bet value is awarded.
All Locked Up symbols stick on the reels while the feature is active.

During the main game and Free Spins, Wilds that are part of a win stay on the reels and shift horizontally one place to the left with each spin. Wilds that shift horizontally during each spin are called Walking Wilds.
